    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a transport mechanism for Unmanned Aircraft
   System (UAS) Network Remote ID (N-RID).  CoAP/CBOR is used for the
   N-RID messaging.  This is secured via either HIP/ESP or DTLS.  HIP/
   ESP or DTLS secure messaging Command-and-Control (C2) for is also
   described.

	 </t>
